Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:12.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,550)\pos(640,505)}Cheers and Sighs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:15.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決行！破滅か？勝利か？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:12.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Which will it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:15.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Abject failure, or victory!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:20.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 始まる\N坂崎の人食い沼との死闘！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:19.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki's duel with the Man-eating Bog begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:22.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:21.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:25.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン 坂崎のオヤジらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:25.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's old man Sakazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:28.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,陽気な博奕だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:27.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He seems like he's having the time of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:31.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも あの台は…\Nシッ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:30.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But that machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:36.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:35.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Got it, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:39.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't just rush in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:39.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐ横に かぶりつくようなマネは\Nやめてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:42.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくんは\Nそろりそろり来てくれればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:43.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just kind of gradually drift toward me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:45.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急いではダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:44.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't rush it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:48.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怪しまれさえしなければ\Nうまくいく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:48.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't attract their attention, we're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:53.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡しも最後の仕上げの開始も\Nうまくやり果たせるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.62,0:00:53.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can pull off the handover and the cleanup!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:57.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また来たぜ クルーンに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:58.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's in the trays again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:01.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,始めてから大して経ってないのに\Nもう３回 いや４回か？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:00.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It never lets anyone through easy, but he's already landed three down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:02.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:05.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ いつもの沼じゃねえ\N大甘だぜ 今日の釘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:05.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Bog isn't usually like this! The pins today must be set for a winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:08.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こりゃあ ひょっとすると\Nひょっとするぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:08.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe! Just maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:10.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ いけ いけ いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.59,0:01:10.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:18.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.58,0:01:18.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きとる きとる きとる！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:22.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は100に１つの特異日\N設定Ａの日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:21.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Today's one in a hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:26.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Setting A... I've never seen this many balls make it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:26.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしも見たことがない\Nこの入り 確率
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:30.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll win it! I'll win that 550—no, that 600 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:30.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てる！５億5000　いや ６億だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:37.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし クリアだ\N最初のハードルはクリア
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:37.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, we're over the first hurdle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:40.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Bog has three hurdles!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:40.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼には３つのハードルがある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:42.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Its first defense:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その第１関門は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:45.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釘の森
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.92,0:01:44.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,the Forest of Pins!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:47.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's through the Forest of Pins!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:47.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釘の森を突破してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:52.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常は60から100に１玉しか\N通過できない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:50.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Normally, only one of every 60 or 100 balls makes it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急所は一番上のぶっこみの釘と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:57.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The key is the top pin, the one it hits first, and the six or seven guarding the path,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:57.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,役モノへの入り口周辺の６～７本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:01:59.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,and then the two by the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:02:00.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして入り口の２本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:02.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But today, they're more forgiving than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:02.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 今日はそれがぬるい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:05.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,寄りがいい　吸い寄せられていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The balls are falling right where we want them! Almost like they're being sucked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:08.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,30に１つは行っている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:07.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One in thirty is making it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:10.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが２番目のハードル
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:10.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the second hurdle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.93,0:02:15.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クルーンの入り口に座り込み\N玉をはじく気まぐれな番人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:15.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Two blocking flippers, guarding the entrance to the trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:20.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,厄介な あまのじゃく\Nランダムに道を閉ざす面倒な関所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:17.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Two troublesome demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An annoying barrier, closing at random!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 長年見てきた\Nおっちゃんの話では
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:27.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But pops has been watching for years, and he says they let about one in three through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:27.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おおよそ３つに１つ\Nクルーンに通す確率らしい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:34.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So one-third of 1/30th of balls make it through the Forest of Pins to the trays.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:31.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とすれば 釘の森を抜けて\Nクルーンにたどり着くのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:34.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,30分の１かける３分の１
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:35.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's one in ninety!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:36.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,90分の１
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:38.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He got another one in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:40.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また入った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All that's left is the big baddie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残るは あの大仰な役モノ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:46.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The real core of the Bog, its toughest part...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:46.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この沼の目玉　最大の難関
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:49.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,難攻不落 最後の砦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:50.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The impregnable fortress, the triple trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３段クルーン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:54.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１段目が３分の１の確率
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:54.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The first lets one of three balls through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:56.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２段目が４分の１
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:56.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The second, one of four.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:03:01.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And the third... The last tray, and the key to the 600 million... One in five.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:03:02.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３段目 入れば６億という\N最終クルーンは５分の１
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:05.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Three by four by five... One in sixty odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:05.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３かける４かける５　60分の１
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:09.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつを落とさなければ\N勝ちはない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:08.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But we can't win without beating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:13.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Factor in the odds of even hitting the trays, and the whole machine is one in 5,400.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:13.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クルーンに届く確率をかけると\N5400分の１
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:19.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,5400玉に１玉 大当たりというのが\N今の沼の計算上の確率
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:19.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How the Bog's set up now, one ball in 5,400 hits the jackpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:29.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お客さま 台を叩くのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:29.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sir, no striking the machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:32.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, I got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:31.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すまんすまん　つい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:42.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:51.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついでにビールくれんか？\Nは？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:50.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, would ya go get me a beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:54.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ネジの巻き直しだ　ビール！\Nあっ はい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:53.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Something to cool me back down! A beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:54.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:58.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This irritation, this impatience... He's mostly faking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:58.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このイラ立ち 焦燥は\Nなかば おっちゃんの演技
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,予定どおりの行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's doing exactly what we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:06.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get this started!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:06.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあて やるか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:08.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:08.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here we go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:13.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よーし いいぞオヤジ\Nめげんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:16.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼むで　井草八幡 力を！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:16.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please! Give me power, Igusa Hachiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:25.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 出すぞ６億\N後押し 頼むで　みんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm getting that 600 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Cheer me on, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Bog! The Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:49.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入った　１段目だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:47.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He made it to the first tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:51.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No, the second!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:51.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２段目も行った！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:01.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日 初の３段目！\Nおおっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The first one to the third today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持っとれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:02.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, get me another!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む　頼む　頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:11.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:13.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:13.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む 来い！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだまだ これからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:26.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got more where that came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:28.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ いけ いけ いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It never goes in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:38.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入らない？\Nああ 入らない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:44.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It never, ever goes in the hole on the bottom tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:40.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの３段目のクルーンの最後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:44.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１番下のクルーンの辺りは\N絶対に入らない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:48.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've proven that on my mockup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:48.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは俺の仮想沼で証明済み
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:52.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の偽物は作りが雑で\Nごくたまに入ったりしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:52.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It isn't quite a perfect copy, so once in a while it makes it in, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:56.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本物の沼はその辺りが\Nきっちり仕上げられていて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:56.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,On the real Bog, they've been very careful
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:59.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玉のコントロール\Nつまりクルーンへの落下速度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:06:03.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,to control the angle and speed the ball enters the bottom tray at.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:03.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,導入角度が寸分違わず 毎回一緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:06.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その結果 その玉は必ず外れる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:07.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Because of this, the ball always misses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:13.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ大体 ５周と５分の１の所で\N玉は推進力を失い 穴に落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:13.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The ball just doesn't have the energy left to make it out of that final 1-in-5 chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:17.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごくたまに\Nその手前か 玉足が伸びて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:20.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Once in a while, it makes it to the hole before the winner,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:20.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり穴の手前の穴まで\N行くことがあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:24.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ブレはその範囲\N決して当たりには届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:24.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,but bends in the tray there make sure it doesn't go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:30.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But on the other hand, if we play with that centrifugal force a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:28.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に言うなら\Nその遠心力の玉の回る力を
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:32.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歪ませることができれば入り得る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:31.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It'll make it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:35.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それには台を開けて\N何か細工するのが一番いいが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:36.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Opening it up and tweaking things would work best,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:41.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの台はカメラと店員によって\N24時間 厳重に監視されている
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:41.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,but that machine has workers and cameras watching it 24/7.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:44.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打つ時以外は\N誰も近づくこともできん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:44.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No one's even allowed close unless they're playing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:49.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となれば 古典的だが\Nこれしかあるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:48.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So this may be the oldest trick in the book, but it's the only one we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,磁石？\Nそう こいつが有効
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:50.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Magnets?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. These'll do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:59.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I hold a strong magnet up to the glass, it'll bend the path of the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:55.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強力な磁石を\Nガラス越しにかざせば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:59.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玉の軌道 遠心力は必ず歪む
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:03.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then the Bog will pay out like it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:03.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなれば あの沼も\N本来の確率で出る台になる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵はそれが怖いから 打つ者に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:08.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're afraid of this happening, so they check players for magnets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:08.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,磁気チェックを\N義務づけているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.47,0:07:12.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 打つ者には厳しくとも\Nやじ馬はノーマーク
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:12.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But they're so focused on the gambler that they ignore the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:14.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノーチェックなんだな これが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They don't check 'em at all. {he's even kinda pointing to the upper-right. lol.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:19.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら渡してもらえばいい\Nノーマークのやじ馬から磁石を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:19.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So I get a magnet from the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:26.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打ち手の横には\Nいつも店員が張り付いている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:26.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's always an employee standing there watching the player.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:29.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Se it can't be out in plain sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 抜き身の磁石じゃダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:31.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっとした工夫が必要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We need a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが これだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:40.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is a fake beer with a magnet in it that we can sneak by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:40.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,底をくり抜き\N磁石を仕込んだゴトビール
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:43.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We swap it while I'm playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:42.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつを勝負の最中に\N交換するのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:44.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うまい手だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:44.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Great idea, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:56.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのすり替え 気づかれなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:54.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The handoff...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not the house, not anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:59.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵にも誰にも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:02.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初の渡しは成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The first part worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:05.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは さりげなく坂崎から離れ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:06.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji nonchalantly walks away from Sakazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:10.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店側の人間の動き 挙動に\N怪しいことがないかをチェック
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:10.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Moving with the crowd, he keeps a poker face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:13.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠巻きに坂崎を見守る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:13.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then he watches Sakazaki from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:19.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's here! My secret weapon is in my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:16.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 来た　わしの武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:19.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秘密兵器がついに わしの手に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here's where it really starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:22.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここからが本当の勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:27.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか カイジくん\N当たれば６億　大変な騒ぎになる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:27.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You ready, Kaiji? When I hit the 600 million, it'll be a real scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:30.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狂喜乱舞 大混乱 乱痴気騒ぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:30.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A flap! A kerfluffle! A pandemonium!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:34.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,While everyone's still confused, you come back
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:34.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その混乱に乗じて\Nカイジくんが戻ってきて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:37.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしのカバンの上に置いた\N磁石入りビールと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:39.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,and swap the fake magnet beer on top of my bag for your own, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:41.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分のビールを再度 すり替え\N現場から離れる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:44.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then get out of there, while the staff gets there and quiets things down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:44.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店の連中が駆けつけて騒ぎを収め
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:49.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その後 わしを身体検査しても\N後の祭り　何も出やせん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:48.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then when they go to check me, it's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They won't find a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:54.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その頃 カイジくんは店の外\N証拠は完全に消える
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:52.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,By that time, you're already outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:54.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The proof's already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:09:01.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう　わしは満座の前で\N身の潔白を証明し 獲得するんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:09:00.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'll come up clean in front of everyone, and then I'll cash in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:05.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,６億を！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All 600 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:10.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大当たりは5400玉に１玉\Nこれが今日の沼の確率
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:10.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One ball in 5,400... That's how many will hit the jackpot in the Bog today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:15.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,5,400 balls at 4,000 yen each is 21,600,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:16.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１玉4000円が5400発で2160万
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:21.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この確率どおりなら 2160万で\N一度は大当たりが出現する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:21.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,At today's odds, there's a jackpot for every 21,600,000 yen pumped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:25.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃんが最終的に\N用意した金は5000万
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:25.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And pops has 50,000,000 yen with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:29.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けるわけがねえ これだけあれば
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:28.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not as long as he has this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:35.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来た 来た 来た！\N３段目だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The third tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:37.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:36.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:43.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right! Activate, magnet beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:44.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし 発動！磁石入りビール
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:49.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歪ませろ 玉の軌道 流れを！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:48.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Bend that ball's path! Its flow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:55.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Bend it! Lead that ball straight up Victory Road!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:51.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,曲げろ　曲げて導け
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:55.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりへと続く\Nビクトリーロードへ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:24.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あー！\Nクッソー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:27.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn! Did it not change the spin enough!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:27.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,回転の歪みが足りなかったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:34.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら もう少し近づけて\N今度は もう少し近づけて…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:32.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then I've just gotta hold it a little bit closer! Just a little closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:36.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's enough. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:37.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もういい　行こう\Nはい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:37.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:42.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ… これで\Nよかったのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:45.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This might be good. They were too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,主任がいる所が近すぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:49.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's better if he hits the jackpot when they're further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:50.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できるなら 大当たりは\N連中が消えてからの方が望ましい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:55.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're paying attention. And it's obvious why if you look at the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:52.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵は警戒している
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:56.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは あのプレーヤーへの\N注意書きを見ても明らか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:11:02.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Rule #1! Cheats such as magnets or batteries are banned!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,注意書き その１
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:02.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,セル 磁石などの\Nあらゆるゴト行為の禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:05.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その２　台を叩く 蹴るなど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:08.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Rule #2! Punching, kicking, or otherwise jolting the machine is banned!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:08.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あらゆる衝撃を与える行為の禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:12.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その３\N故意 不可抗力にかかわらず
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:17.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Rule #3! Whether intentional or not, modifying, damaging, or oiling balls is banned!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:17.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玉に何らかの細工 傷を付けたり\N油を塗ったりすることは禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:20.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So they're afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:20.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 敵は恐れてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:24.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３段目 クルーンの回転が\N歪むことを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:23.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Afraid someone will mess with the third tray...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:26.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And of course, there's this last part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:27.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして極めつけは この一文
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:30.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,For customers who obey these rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:30.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,以上のことを\Nお守りいただけるお客様には
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:33.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その方がプレーしている限り
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:36.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,no matter what the cost to this casino is,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:36.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんなに当カジノにとって\N不都合であろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:39.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガラス戸を開けての釘調整等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:39.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,as long as they play we will never perform acts such as
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:42.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一切の操作 変更はいたしません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:42.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,removing the glass and modifying the pin layout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心してお遊びください
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please play with full confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:47.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This confidence, this conviction!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:47.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この自信 確信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:52.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言い換えるなら ３段目は\Nクルーンの絶対性さえ保てれば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:53.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's because as long as the third tray keeps working, no one will ever win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:56.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100％入らない\Nそういう敵の自信が透けて見える
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can see right through them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:59.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら 逆にありなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:03.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's how I know this magnet-beer plan to mess with the third tray has a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:03.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３段目を無力化する\Nこの磁石入りビール作戦が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:12.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki's first ten million packy are spent!
