Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:40.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He wants more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:44.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Bring another ten million packy!
