Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:12.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, he did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:16.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこかで都合をつけたのか\Nもう2000か3000万は…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:16.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Somehow, he got his hands on another twenty or thirty...
