Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:27.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Another 10,000,000 packy gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Will that be all for today, sir?
