Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がついてないんだ 奴ら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:28.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They haven't realized yet!
