Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:44.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,As long as we have the magnets!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:47.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは まあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:47.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:50.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら… なら何の問題もない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:50.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So there's no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:55.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Quit joking around! There's no reason to quit when we're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:55.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 やめることはない　そうさ\N冗談じゃない あと少しなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:59.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,磁石入りビールを使いだして\N６回 ３段目に運んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:18:00.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've made it to the third tray six times since I started with the magnet beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:05.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５分の１の確率だ\Nもう来る頃だ　次か その次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It has one in five odds, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's overdue! Next time, or the time after!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:10.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし どうするつもりだ\Nブロックされたら？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:08.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And what are you gonna do when they use the block?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵はまだ策を持ってんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:14.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They still have tricks up their sleeve. Probably an impenetrable defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:15.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく鉄壁に近い防御を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:17.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを使われたら終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Once they use that, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:21.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら ここまでがどうだろうと\Nもう負けは見えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:20.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what's happened, we're beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:24.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That does sound pretty ominous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:24.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その点は確かに不気味だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:28.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし よく考えたら\N敵は待ってくれている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:28.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But if you think about it, they're waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:32.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 待ってくれてるんだろ？\Nそのブロックとやらを
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:32.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're holding off on that block.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:36.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So we still have a chance, right, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:34.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出る　今なら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:36.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違うか？カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:40.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら撤退は そのブロックを\Nされてからでも遅くない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:40.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So there's no point in quitting until the block comes out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:43.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,作戦タイム終了だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're done planning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:45.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ？\Nいいのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:49.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on. You're playing with someone else's money now. The money you "borrowed".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:50.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここから先は人の金\Nくすねてきた金なんだぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:54.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう意味じゃ分岐点\N分かれ道なんだよ 今が
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:54.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You've got a choice to make here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:57.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 やめれば少なくとも\N後ろに手が回ることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:57.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you quit now, you can at least stay a free man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:00.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間に合うんだ まだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:18:59.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You still have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:04.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間に合う？\Nそうさ　まだ間に合う
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I still have a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:03.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You still have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:06.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:06.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何に？\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:09.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間に合うって 何に？\Nだ… だから その…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:08.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, I still have a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:15.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカヤロー！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:22.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you understand? My 20 million... My 20 million is all gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってんのか？ああ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:22.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000万… 2000万…\N2000万 いかれちまったんやぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:25.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, I still have a chance!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:25.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今さら何が間に合うっていうんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:30.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I told you! That money was everything I had! It was my future!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:28.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ったやろ あの金が全てやって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:33.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの金がわしの未来\N希望の全てなんや
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,My only hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:34.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You think I can wash my hands of it here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:36.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,済むか！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:41.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've lost it all! I can't quit without winning it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:39.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すりました 負けました\Nかからんかったで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引き下がれるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:45.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got to win! I can't turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝たにゃならん\N取り返さにゃならんのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:47.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何としても！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:47.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:50.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:54.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki resumes his challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:54.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負再開　坂崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:59.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全財産2000万を使い果たし\Nついに手を出す他人の金
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:59.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Having bet his own twenty million, he begins to bet out of someone else's pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:03.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,緊急調達したマル秘の金 3000万！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:02.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The thirty million  he "secured" in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:08.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:09.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けられない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:13.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして突入\N極限を超えた狂気の世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:13.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He dives into a world of madness! beyond all limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:15.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔の領域へ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The devil's territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:30.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji the Movie 2 opens November 5th!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:32.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:35.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The impossible pachinko machine, the Bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:46.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To defeat this monster, Kaiji takes on the casino's manager Ichijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:52.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Original author Nobuyuki Fukumoto joins the writing staff
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:56.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,in this new story of life-or-death games.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:21:03.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This fall, the ultimate entertainment sets Japan abuzz.
